svg.title: bookholmes
svg.text: Detective Sherlock Holmes and Dr. John Watson join forces to investigate a mysterious murder at Buckingham Palace. It seems like an open-and-shut case as all signs point to Professor James Mo-riarty, the criminal mastermind and longtime nemesis of the crime-solving duo.
2018 | Dir. Etan Cohen Sherlock: Will FerrelWatson: John C Reilly
